<l>tuñcuṅkāṟ ṟōṇmēla rāki viḻikkuṅkāl </l>
<l>neñcatta rāvar viraintu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>When I am asleep he rests on my shoulders, (but) when I awake he hastens into my soul.</l>
